{
  "stem": "1216.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think we probably all have them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it was-- it was much more important to teach us not to lie anymore and not to steal anymore, and, yes, this is a banana, and no, you can't take it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The rest kind of went by the wayside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The adults also had to adjust.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably within the year.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know that my-- either of my parents took me apart and said, now, you've done this, and this, and this, and now that's no good anymore.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when something came up, I think that's when I got a lecture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let's just say that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know-- I said I hadn't done something that I had, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At this point, I can honestly say, I don't lie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would rather say nothing than to say an untruth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Equally, I don't cheat, and I don't steal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was easier to learn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not right away because we came home in June, and that's summer vacation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dutch elementary schools, then and possibly now, started in August.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in August, I went back to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, again, there were problems there because when we left, when we were deported, I was in second grade-- had pretty well finished second grade.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But third and fourth never happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So now I was stuck in fifth grade, which was more age appropriate, but I hadn't the foggiest idea what had happened in the last two years.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And for that matter, to a great extent, I still don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I haven't needed what I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I can look up what I don't know, but the fact remains, I never learned it.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
